38:30.880 --> 38:33.119
- The engine's back on.
- But we're not moving.

38:39.880 --> 38:40.800
He's cut us off!

38:49.280 --> 38:50.519
The engine is overheating.

38:52.199 --> 38:53.960
- What's going on?
- It's Charlie.

38:54.960 --> 38:56.400
He's trying to blow up the ship.

39:08.360 --> 39:10.199
My name is Olivia Jackson,

39:12.519 --> 39:16.840
daughter of the late Sarah Jackson,
who died at the Polaris V Station.

39:19.960 --> 39:24.039
I believe Arthur Wilde
was responsible for my mother's death.

39:25.840 --> 39:28.519
And his crew helped cover it up
to protect the research.

39:31.320 --> 39:34.760
<i>When I discovered Arthur Wilde</i>
<i>and his team were going to Polaris VI,</i>

39:35.199 --> 39:38.000
<i>I managed to join</i>
<i>under the name of Margaret Mitchell.</i>

39:39.199 --> 39:42.039
It was then that I killed them all,
one by one,

39:42.119 --> 39:43.960
leaving only Arthur Wilde alive.

39:47.440 --> 39:49.760
I spared his life for the sole purpose

39:49.840 --> 39:52.320
of framing him
for the murders I perpetrated.

39:56.000 --> 39:57.400
I did it for my mother.

40:08.159 --> 40:09.440
And I would do it again.
